text: Borve () is a village in Harris in the Outer Hebrides, Scotland. Borve is also within the parish of Harris, and is on the A859. ==References== ==External links== *Canmore - Harris, Borve, Borve Lodge site record *Canmore - Harris, Borve, Borve House site record Category:Villages in Harris, Outer Hebrides
